targets.rawSql:
SELECT 
    toStartOfMonth(time) AS month,  -- Группируем по началу месяца
    (max(totaldistance) - min(totaldistance)) / 1000 AS monthly_km  -- Разница в километрах за месяц
FROM 
    metrics
WHERE 
    $__timeFilter(time)
    AND totaldistance != 0
GROUP BY 
    month
HAVING 
    monthly_km >= 1
ORDER BY 
    month

SELECT 
    toStartOfMinute(time) AS time_interval,  -- округляем время до минут (можно настроить на более мелкие интервалы)
    totaldistance / 1000 as total_km
FROM 
    metrics
WHERE 
    $__timeFilter(time)
    and totaldistance != 0
ORDER BY 
    time_interval

SELECT (max(totaldistance) - min(totaldistance)) / 1000
FROM metrics
WHERE $__timeFilter(time)
AND totaldistance != 0

SELECT 
    toDate(time) AS date,  -- Группируем по дате (без времени)
    (max(totaldistance) - min(totaldistance)) / 1000 AS daily_km  -- Разница в километрах за день
FROM 
    metrics
WHERE 
    $__timeFilter(time)
    AND totaldistance != 0
GROUP BY 
    date
ORDER BY 
    date
